(923, 'Groundhog Day', 'Romantic comedy,Romance,', 'February 2nd keeps repeating for a TV weatherman sent to watch the groundhog in Punxsutawney, Pa.', '598', 1993, '2020-10-24T00:00Z', '2020-10-24T01:45Z', '105', 'MV000363120000', '14569', '1993-02-12', 'en', 'Phil (Bill Murray), a weatherman, is out to cover the annual emergence of the groundhog from its hole. He gets caught in a blizzard that he didn\'t predict and finds himself trapped in a time warp. He is doomed to relive the same day over and over again until he gets it right.', '74320'),
