(926, 'Mission: Impossible -- Fallout', 'Action,Adventure,Thriller,', 'Ethan Hunt and the IMF team must prevent terrorists from detonating three nuclear devices.', '597', 2018, '2020-10-24T00:00Z', '2020-10-24T02:30Z', '150', 'MV009499780000', '13492451', '2018-07-27', 'en', 'Ethan Hunt and the IMF team join forces with CIA assassin August Walker to prevent a disaster of epic proportions. Arms dealer John Lark and a group of terrorists known as the Apostles plan to use three plutonium cores for a simultaneous nuclear attack on the Vatican, Jerusalem and Mecca, Saudi Arabia. When the weapons go missing, Ethan and his crew find themselves in a desperate race against time to prevent them from falling into the wrong hands.', '73075'),
(927, 'Forbidden Planet', 'Science fiction,', 'Astronaut (Leslie Nielsen) and crew land on Altair-4 in 2200.', '1248', 1956, '2020-10-24T00:00Z', '2020-10-24T02:10Z', '130', 'MV000037660000', '2306', '1956-03-15', 'en', 'In this sci-fi classic, a spacecraft travels to the distant planet Altair IV to discover the fate of a group of scientists sent there decades earlier. When Commander John J. Adams (Leslie Nielsen) and his crew arrive, they discover only two people: Dr. Morbius (Walter Pidgeon) and his daughter, Altaira (Anne Francis), who was born on the remote planet. Soon, Adams begins to uncover the mystery of what happened on Altair IV, and why Morbius and Altaira are the sole survivors.', '59218'),
