(929, 'Ride Beyond Vengeance', 'Western,', 'Buffalo hunter (Chuck Connors) robbed and branded by banker (Michael Rennie) and henchmen.', '1260', 1966, '2020-10-24T00:00Z', '2020-10-24T02:30Z', '150', 'MV000020980000', '1306', '1966', 'en', 'Following an 11-year stay as a buffalo hunter in Kansas, Jonas Trapp (Chuck Connors) is finally on the way home to his wife, Jessie (Kathryn Hays), with the $17,000 he has saved up. Unfortunately, he happens to run into a group of bandits led by Brooks Durham (Michael Rennie) ; they beat him, brand him and steal all of his money. Now, returning home without a dollar to his name, Jonas finds Jessie has moved on to another man -- namely, Brooks Durham.', '43926'),
