(1020, 'Legally Blonde', 'Comedy,', 'A sorority queen (Reese Witherspoon) enrolls in Harvard to win back her boyfriend.', '557', 2001, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:35Z', '95', 'MV001099680000', '28004', '2001-07-13', 'en', 'Elle Woods (Reese Witherspoon) has it all. She wants nothing more than to be Mrs. Warner Huntington III. But there is one thing stopping him (Matthew Davis) from proposing: She is too blond. Elle rallies all of her resources and gets into Harvard, determined to win him back.', '25272'),
(1021, 'The Money Pit', 'Comedy,', 'A New York lawyer and his girlfriend buy a mansion cheap, then find it needs extensive work.', '558', 1986, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:35Z', '95', 'MV000199770000', '9141', '1986-09-26', 'en', 'Young lovers Walter (Tom Hanks) and Anna (Shelley Long) are house-sitting the New York City apartment owned by Max (Alexander Godunov), Anna\'s ex-husband, who suddenly decides to toss them out. Needing a new home, they settle on buying a country estate outside the city, which is available for a suspiciously low price. It soon becomes apparent why, as doors fall off their hinges, staircases come tumbling down and a bathtub falls through the floor. The couple\'s relationship suffers similarly.', '25274'),
(1022, 'Home Alone 2: Lost in New York', 'Comedy,Children,Holiday,', 'A left-behind boy (Macaulay Culkin) battles two burglars (Joe Pesci, Daniel Stern) he faced before.', '521', 1992, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '120', 'MV000359530000', '14385', '1992-11-15', 'en', 'After snarky youth Kevin McCallister (Macaulay Culkin) loses track of his father at the airport, he mistakenly gets on a plane headed for New York City -- while the rest of the McCallisters fly to Florida. Now alone in the Big Apple, Kevin cons his way into a room at the Plaza Hotel and begins his usual antics. But when Kevin discovers that the Sticky Bandits (Joe Pesci, Daniel Stern) are on the loose, he struggles to stop them from robbing an elderly man\'s toy store just before Christmas.', '16619'),
(1023, 'Tone-Deaf', 'Horror,Dark comedy,', 'Olive is exposed to the dark underbelly of rural America when she spends a weekend in the country.', '572', 2019, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:30Z', '90', 'MV012446810000', '16716541', '2019-03-10', 'en', 'After a string of bad relationships and work failures, Olive leaves for a weekend in the country, only to discover the shocking dark underbelly of rural America.', '17663'),
(1024, 'Ad Astra', 'Science fiction,Adventure,Thriller,', 'An astronaut journeys across the universe to uncover the truth about his father\'s doomed mission.', '516', 2019, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T04:05Z', '125', 'MV011767610000', '15724355', '2019-08-29', 'en', 'Thirty years ago, Clifford McBride led a voyage into deep space, but the ship and crew were never heard from again. Now his son -- a fearless astronaut -- must embark on a daring mission to Neptune to uncover the truth about his missing father and a mysterious power surge that threatens the stability of the universe.', '18431'),
(1025, 'Hall Pass', 'Comedy,', 'Two men get permission from their wives to spend one week doing whatever they please.', '533', 2011, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:45Z', '105', 'MV003358360000', '8329415', '2011-02-25', 'en', 'Best friends Rick (Owen Wilson) and Fred (Jason Sudeikis) each have been married for a long time, and they are showing signs of restlessness. To revitalize their marriages, their wives (Jenna Fischer, Christina Applegate) grant them one week to do whatever they please, no questions asked. At first, the deal sounds like a dream come true, but as the week marches on, the two friends discover that their expectations are wildly out of sync with reality.', '18433'),
(1026, 'Dead Silence', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'A man returns to his haunted hometown to unravel the mystery surrounding his wife\'s death.', '534', 2007, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:30Z', '90', 'MV001867680000', '164673', '2007-03-16', 'en', 'After his wife meets a grisly end, Jamie Ashen (Ryan Kwanten) returns to their creepy hometown of Ravens Fair to unravel the mystery of her murder. Once there, he discovers the legend of Mary Shaw (Joan Heney), a murdered ventriloquist whose eerie presence still looms over the town. As he desperately digs for answers, Jamie encounters the curse that took his wife\'s life and threatens his own.', '18435'),
(1027, 'My Father, My Kidnapper', 'Thriller,', 'When her mother suddenly disappears, Casey must face the dark secrets of the past to find her.', '076', 2019, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '120', 'MV013489810000', '17644369', '2019', 'en', 'When her mother Jane suddenly disappears, Casey must face the dark secrets of the past to find her before it\'s too late.', '18480'),
