(1036, 'Picture a Perfect Christmas', 'Romance,Drama,Holiday,', 'A photographer gets involved with helping a neighbor look after his young nephew.', '039', 2019, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '120', 'MV013016240000', '17355906', '2019-10-23', 'en', 'A photographer returns home to take care of her grandmother and gets involved with helping a neighbor look after his young nephew.', '11221'),
