(1038, 'The Cable Guy', 'Comedy,', 'An unbalanced cable-TV installer (Jim Carrey) plagues an architect (Matthew Broderick).', '133', 1996, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '120', 'MV000465540000', '18112', '1996-12-03', 'en', 'Oddball cable installer Chip Douglas (Jim Carrey) attempts to strike up a friendship with customer Steven Kovacs (Matthew Broderick) by offering him premium channels at no cost. When Steven rebuffs Chip\'s frequent need for companionship, Chip goes from a mildly eccentric acquaintance to a full-fledged psycho stalker. Though it\'s increasingly apparent to Steven that the cable guy is dangerous, convincing his friends, family and the authorities of that is another matter entirely.', '18822'),
(1039, 'Tyler Perry\'s Meet the Browns', 'Comedy drama,Romance,', 'A woman (Angela Bassett) meets her late father\'s uproarious family for the first time.', '555', 2008, '2020-10-24T02:00Z', '2020-10-24T03:45Z', '105', 'MV010365390000', '175030', '2008-03-21', 'en', 'Single mother Brenda (Angela Bassett) suddenly loses her job, then she receives news that the father she never met is dead. With nothing to lose, she gathers her brood and heads to Georgia, where she meets her father\'s uproarious family for the first time and finds the tentative beginnings of a new romance.', '20622'),
