(1050, 'The Shootist', 'Western,', 'People pester an old, dying gunfighter (John Wayne) rooming with a widow in 1901 Nevada.', '640', 1976, '2020-10-24T02:10Z', '2020-10-24T03:55Z', '105', 'MV000054340000', '3260', '1976-08-11', 'en', 'J.B. Books (John Wayne, in his final film role) is an aging gunfighter diagnosed with cancer who comes to Nevada at the turn of the 20th century. Renting a room from widowed Bond Rogers (Lauren Bacall) and her son Gillom (Ron Howard), Books is confronted by several people of questionable motives, including a man seeking to avenge his brother\'s death and a few who are looking to profit from Books\' notoriety. Not wanting to die a quiet, painful death, Books devises a plan to go out with a bang.', '33668'),
(1051, 'League of Gods', 'Fantasy,Adventure,Action,', 'El rey Zhou se convierte gradualmente en un tirano por la influencia de Daji.', '973', 2016, '2020-10-24T02:10Z', '2020-10-24T04:10Z', '120', 'MV010283960000', '13103284', '2016-07-29', 'en', 'El rey Zhou se convierte gradualmente en un tirano por la influencia de Daji, el espíritu de una bruja disfrazado como el de uno de sus concubinas.', '76408'),
(1052, 'The Thing From Another World', 'Science fiction,', 'Arctic scientists find an alien (James Arness) that feeds on blood.', '1248', 1951, '2020-10-24T02:10Z', '2020-10-24T04:05Z', '115', 'MV000913320000', '2300', '1951', 'en-GB', 'When scientist Dr. Carrington (Robert Cornthwaite) reports a UFO near his North Pole research base, the Air Force sends in a team under Capt. Patrick Hendry (Kenneth Tobey) to investigate. What they find is a wrecked spaceship and a humanoid creature (James Arness) frozen in the ice. They bring their discovery back to the base, but Carrington and Hendry disagree over what to do with it. Meanwhile, the creature is accidentally thawed and begins wreaking havoc.', '59218');
