(1135, 'Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby', 'Comedy,', 'Jealousy inflames a NASCAR driver (Will Ferrell) when a French rival arrives on the scene.', '112', 2006, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '120', 'MV001784370000', '159752', '2006-08-04', 'en', 'NASCAR superstar Ricky Bobby (Will Ferrell) is at the top of his game; adored by fans, a trophy wife by his side, and incredible wealth. But Ricky loses it all when French Formula One champion Jean Girard (Sacha Baron Cohen) roars onto the scene. Ricky, with the help of his ruthless father, must pull himself out of the depths of despair and restore his honor on the racetrack.', '10153'),
(1136, 'G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra', 'Action,Adventure,', 'The G.I. Joe team uses the latest technology in its battle against a mysterious organization.', '058', 2009, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '120', 'MV002135140000', '176171', '2009-08-07', 'en', 'Armed with the latest in military and spy technology, the team of elite soldiers known as G.I. Joe travel around the globe to wherever their services are needed. In their latest assignment Gen. Hawk (Dennis Quaid), Duke (Channing Tatum) and the rest of the G.I. Joe team take on Destro (Christopher Eccleston), a corrupt arms dealer, and fight the growing threat of the mysterious Cobra organization.', '11097'),
(1137, 'G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra', 'Action,Adventure,', 'The G.I. Joe team uses the latest technology in its battle against a mysterious organization.', '111', 2009, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '120', 'MV002135140000', '176171', '2009-08-07', 'en', 'Armed with the latest in military and spy technology, the team of elite soldiers known as G.I. Joe travel around the globe to wherever their services are needed. In their latest assignment Gen. Hawk (Dennis Quaid), Duke (Channing Tatum) and the rest of the G.I. Joe team take on Destro (Christopher Eccleston), a corrupt arms dealer, and fight the growing threat of the mysterious Cobra organization.', '11097'),
(1138, 'XXX: State of the Union', 'Action,Adventure,Thriller,', 'Agent XXX (Ice Cube) must thwart a plot to depose the president.', '609', 2005, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T05:44Z', '104', 'MV001563460000', '35709', '2005-04-29', 'en', 'When the government finds out that a group of terrorists has infiltrated its ranks, and the group is being trained by high-ranking official George Deckert (Willem Dafoe), NSA Agent Augustus Gibbons (Samuel L. Jackson) hires an ex-con to bring down the nefarious plot. Thinking he can trust no one in the government, Augustus springs Darius Stone (Ice Cube), who once trained under him, from prison. Although Darius is a loose cannon, Augustus is convinced he is the only man for the job.', '17125'),
(1139, 'John Wick: Chapter 3 -- Parabellum', 'Action,Thriller,', 'Hit man John Wick fights for his life when he becomes the target of the world\'s top assassins.', '535', 2019, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:10Z', '130', 'MV010389600000', '14568731', '2019-05-15', 'en', 'After gunning down a member of the High Table -- the shadowy international assassin\'s guild -- legendary hit man John Wick finds himself stripped of the organization\'s protective services. Now stuck with a $14 million bounty on his head, Wick must fight his way through the streets of New York as he becomes the target of the world\'s most ruthless killers.', '25622'),
(1140, 'Miss Peregrine\'s Home for Peculiar Children', 'Fantasy,Adventure,Action,Mystery,Drama,', 'A teen discovers a secret refuge on an island where children have special powers and hidden enemies.', '068', 2016, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '180', 'MV008008720000', '12109404', '2016-09-30', 'en', 'When his beloved grandfather leaves Jake clues to a mystery that spans different worlds and times, he finds a magical place known as Miss Peregrine\'s School for Peculiar Children. But the mystery and danger deepen as he gets to know the residents and learns about their special powers - and their terrifying enemies. Ultimately, Jake discovers that only his own special peculiarity can save his new friends. Based on the novel \"Miss Peregrine\'s Home For Peculiar Children,\" written by Ransom Riggs.', '14321'),
(1141, 'Miss Peregrine\'s Home for Peculiar Children', 'Fantasy,Adventure,Action,Mystery,Drama,', 'A teen discovers a secret refuge on an island where children have special powers and hidden enemies.', '108', 2016, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '180', 'MV008008720000', '12109404', '2016-09-30', 'en', 'When his beloved grandfather leaves Jake clues to a mystery that spans different worlds and times, he finds a magical place known as Miss Peregrine\'s School for Peculiar Children. But the mystery and danger deepen as he gets to know the residents and learns about their special powers - and their terrifying enemies. Ultimately, Jake discovers that only his own special peculiarity can save his new friends. Based on the novel \"Miss Peregrine\'s Home For Peculiar Children,\" written by Ransom Riggs.', '14321'),
(1142, 'Mary Queen of Scots', 'Biography,Historical drama,', 'Chronicles Mary Stuart\'s attempt to overthrow her cousin Elizabeth I, Queen of England.', '532', 2018, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:05Z', '125', 'MV011087680000', '15413861', '2018-11-15', 'en-GB', 'Queen of France at 16 and widowed at 18, Mary Stuart defies pressure to remarry. Instead, she returns to her native Scotland to reclaim her rightful throne. But Scotland and England fall under the rule of the compelling Elizabeth I. Each young Queen beholds her sister in fear and fascination. Rivals in power and in love, and female regents in a masculine world, the two must decide how to play the game of marriage versus independence.', '10121'),
(1143, 'The Kitchen', 'Crime drama,', 'Three women take over the Hell\'s Kitchen section of New York for their imprisoned gangster husbands.', '513', 2019, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T05:45Z', '105', 'MV012397240000', '16645500', '2019-08-09', 'en', 'Between 8th Ave. and the Hudson River, the Irish mafia runs 20 blocks of a tough New York City neighborhood known as Hell\'s Kitchen. But for mob wives Kathy, Ruby and Claire, things are about to take a dramatic and radical turn. When the FBI sends their husbands to prison, the three women take business into their own hands by running the rackets and taking out the competition.', '10243'),
(1144, 'Pyaar Mein Twist', 'Romance,', 'Two widowed businesspeople (Rishi Kapoor, Dimple Kapadia) meet and fall in love.', '1532', 2005, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '180', 'MV004626850000', '8271045', '2005', 'hi', 'A businesswoman (Dimple Kapadia) does a great job managing her family and her company but cannot manage her heart.', '52285'),
