(1151, 'Trapped by My Father\'s Killer', 'Thriller,', 'A woman is held captive in her home by the man she sent to jail for murdering her father and fiancé.', '076', 2020, '2020-10-24T04:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '120', 'MV014539270000', '18806856', '2020-10-23', 'en', 'Five years after sending Louis to jail for the murder of her father and fiancé, Diana returns home to find that he has escaped from prison and has come to confront her. However, Louis wants to convince her that she put an innocent man away.', '18480'),
