(1177, 'William y Catherine: un romance real', 'Docudrama,', 'La historia de amor entre el príncipe William y Kate Middleton, paso a paso hasta el altar.', '849', 2011, '2020-10-24T04:30Z', '2020-10-24T05:40Z', '70', 'MV012172260000', '8612720', '2011-08-27', 'es-ES', 'La historia de amor entre el príncipe William y Kate Middleton: su ruptura, la reconciliación, el noviazgo, los preparativos de la boda y los consejos que la reina le dio a su nieto.', '79605'),
(1178, 'Project X', 'Comedy,', 'Three high-school seniors try to make a name for themselves by throwing an unforgettable party.', '537', 2012, '2020-10-24T04:34Z', '2020-10-24T06:02Z', '88', 'MV003709630000', '8818865', '2012-03-02', 'en', 'Thomas (Thomas Mann), Costa (Oliver Cooper) and JB (Jonathan Daniel Brown) are three anonymous high-school seniors who are determined to finally make their mark. But how to make themselves unforgettable in the annals of high-school history? With an epic party, of course! The idea is innocent enough, but nothing could prepare the three friends for this shindig. As word of the soiree\'s awesomeness spreads, dreams are ruined, records are blemished, and legends are born.', '25620'),
(1179, 'La piel de ayer', 'Adventure,', 'Las consecuencias del huracán María impulsan a un joven a buscar agua para su familia.', '524', 2018, '2020-10-24T04:34Z', '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '26', 'MV012533560000', '16824635', '2018', 'es', 'Las consecuencias del huracán María impulsan a un joven viudo a luchar contra las dificultades y cumplir con sus deberes familiares. En medio de la crisis se propone a buscar agua.', '24575'),
(1180, 'Paranormal Activity 2', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'Video cameras capture the supernatural events that plague a Southern California family.', '553', 2010, '2020-10-24T04:35Z', '2020-10-24T06:15Z', '100', 'MV002784240000', '8077746', '2010-10-22', 'en', 'When the Reys move into their new Southern California home, little do they realize that the house is already occupied. After coming home one day to find the house in disarray -- but with no signs of forced entry or robbery -- they install a video surveillance system to catch the perpetrators. But nothing prepares them for what happens next.', '16153'),
(1181, 'Tusk', 'Horror,', 'An American podcaster ventures into the Canadian wilds to interview a man who has a dark secret.', '556', 2014, '2020-10-24T04:35Z', '2020-10-24T06:30Z', '115', 'MV006002170000', '10905368', '2014-09-19', 'en', 'A U.S. podcaster (Justin Long) ventures into the Canadian wilderness to interview an old man (Michael Parks) who has an extraordinary past, and the American learns the man has a dark secret involving a walrus.', '25270'),
(1182, 'Date Movie', 'Romantic comedy,', 'Obstacles litter a hopeless romantic\'s (Alyson Hannigan) path to true love.', '522', 2006, '2020-10-24T04:35Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '85', 'MV001677700000', '159830', '2006-02-17', 'en', 'Julia (Alyson Hannigan), a hopeless romantic, finally finds the man of her dreams: British gentleman Grant Fonkyerdoder. But she and her beau face many hurdles that they must overcome on the way to the altar. First, each has to meet the other\'s parents, then they must consult a wedding planner and foil the plot of beautiful -- but jealous -- Andy, who desperately wants to spoil her best friend\'s wedding.', '18430'),
(1183, 'Vértigo', 'Drama,', 'Ocurre una tragedia familiar cuando una mujer es seducida por el novio de su hija.', '980', 1946, '2020-10-24T04:35Z', '2020-10-24T06:00Z', '85', 'MV001175500000', '75127', '1946-02-14', 'es', 'Ocurre una tragedia familiar cuando una mujer es seducida por el novio de su hija.', '35401'),
(1184, 'Higher Learning', 'Drama,', 'Racial tensions between blacks and white supremacists divide freshmen college students.', '604', 1995, '2020-10-24T04:36Z', '2020-10-24T06:47Z', '131', 'MV000412680000', '16342', '1995-01-11', 'en', 'In John Singleton\'s powerful portrait of college life in the 1990s, a group of incoming freshmen at Columbus University -- including varsity athlete Malik Williams (Omar Epps), awkward outcast Remy (Michael Rapaport) and wide-eyed Kristen Connor (Kristy Swanson) -- struggle to find themselves and adjust to newfound independence. When Remy finds acceptance among a group of neo-Nazis, tensions rise even higher on a campus already divided along racial, socio-economic and gender lines.', '14870'),
(1185, 'Resident Evil: Retribution', 'Horror,Action,', 'New allies and old friends aid Alice in her search for those responsible for the T-virus outbreak.', '582', 2012, '2020-10-24T04:36Z', '2020-10-24T06:14Z', '98', 'MV003903890000', '9128231', '2012-09-14', 'en', 'As Umbrella Corp.\'s deadly T-virus continues to turn the world\'s population into legions of flesh-eating zombies, Alice (Milla Jovovich), the human race\'s last hope, awakes deep within Umbrella\'s secret operations facility. The further she delves into the complex, the more of her mysterious past is unveiled. Her global hunt for those responsible for the outbreak leads to a mind-blowing revelation; Aided by friends old and new, Alice fights to escape from a world on the edge of oblivion.', '16311'),
(1186, 'Ghost Rider: Spirit of Vengeance', 'Action,Fantasy,', 'A secret sect hires Johnny Blaze (Nicolas Cage) to save a boy from Satan (Ciarán Hinds).', '602', 2011, '2020-10-24T04:36Z', '2020-10-24T06:15Z', '99', 'MV003685660000', '8786426', '2011', 'en', 'Now hiding out in Eastern Europe, Johnny Blaze (Nicolas Cage) is still struggling with the curse of the Ghost Rider -- the devil\'s bounty hunter. Johnny meets a priest named Moreau (Idris Elba), who asks Johnny to find a boy named Danny (Fergus Riordan) and bring him back. But there\'s a catch -- Satan (Ciarán Hinds) is looking for the boy too, and has a personal stake in the matter. But if Johnny can find Danny first and save the boy\'s soul, there\'s a chance Johnny can save his own soul as well.', '10178'),
(1187, 'War for the Planet of the Apes', 'Science fiction,Action,Adventure,', 'A colonel leads his troops in a deadly battle against Caesar and his army of intelligent apes.', '083', 2017, '2020-10-24T04:40Z', '2020-10-24T07:30Z', '170', 'MV008029970000', '12126545', '2017-07-14', 'en', 'Caesar (Andy Serkis) and his apes are forced into a deadly conflict with an army of humans led by a ruthless colonel (Woody Harrelson). After the apes suffer unimaginable losses, Caesar wrestles with his darker instincts and begins his own mythic quest to avenge his kind. As the journey finally brings them face to face, Caesar and the colonel are pitted against each other in an epic battle that will determine the fate of both of their species and the future of the planet.', '14988'),
(1188, 'War for the Planet of the Apes', 'Science fiction,Action,Adventure,', 'A colonel leads his troops in a deadly battle against Caesar and his army of intelligent apes.', '632', 2017, '2020-10-24T04:40Z', '2020-10-24T07:30Z', '170', 'MV008029970000', '12126545', '2017-07-14', 'en', 'Caesar (Andy Serkis) and his apes are forced into a deadly conflict with an army of humans led by a ruthless colonel (Woody Harrelson). After the apes suffer unimaginable losses, Caesar wrestles with his darker instincts and begins his own mythic quest to avenge his kind. As the journey finally brings them face to face, Caesar and the colonel are pitted against each other in an epic battle that will determine the fate of both of their species and the future of the planet.', '14988'),
(1189, 'Vertical Limit', 'Thriller,', 'A climber (Chris O\'Donnell) must rescue his sister (Robin Tunney) stranded by an avalanche.', '603', 2000, '2020-10-24T04:42Z', '2020-10-24T06:50Z', '128', 'MV001008900000', '26712', '2000-12-03', 'en', 'Feeling responsible for his father\'s death, which occurred during a climbing expedition, Peter Garrett (Chris O\'Donnell) has quit the pursuit in favor of photography, while his sister, Annie (Robin Tunney), has become a top climber. After Annie is hired by wealthy businessman Elliot Vaughn (Bill Paxton) to lead a trek, inclement weather causes the crew to become trapped. Facing his fears, Peter assembles a rescue team, including experienced climber Montgomery Wick (Scott Glenn), to save them.', '14871'),
(1190, 'The Thing From Another World', 'Science fiction,', 'Arctic scientists find an alien (James Arness) that feeds on blood.', '064', 1951, '2020-10-24T04:45Z', '2020-10-24T06:30Z', '105', 'MV000913320000', '2300', '1951', 'en-GB', 'When scientist Dr. Carrington (Robert Cornthwaite) reports a UFO near his North Pole research base, the Air Force sends in a team under Capt. Patrick Hendry (Kenneth Tobey) to investigate. What they find is a wrecked spaceship and a humanoid creature (James Arness) frozen in the ice. They bring their discovery back to the base, but Carrington and Hendry disagree over what to do with it. Meanwhile, the creature is accidentally thawed and begins wreaking havoc.', '12852'),
(1191, 'The Thing From Another World', 'Science fiction,', 'Arctic scientists find an alien (James Arness) that feeds on blood.', '631', 1951, '2020-10-24T04:45Z', '2020-10-24T06:30Z', '105', 'MV000913320000', '2300', '1951', 'en-GB', 'When scientist Dr. Carrington (Robert Cornthwaite) reports a UFO near his North Pole research base, the Air Force sends in a team under Capt. Patrick Hendry (Kenneth Tobey) to investigate. What they find is a wrecked spaceship and a humanoid creature (James Arness) frozen in the ice. They bring their discovery back to the base, but Carrington and Hendry disagree over what to do with it. Meanwhile, the creature is accidentally thawed and begins wreaking havoc.', '12852'),
(1192, 'Keeping the Faith', 'Romantic comedy,', 'A rabbi (Ben Stiller) and a priest (Edward Norton) each fall for an old friend (Jenna Elfman).', '540', 2000, '2020-10-24T04:50Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '130', 'MV000875460000', '25147', '2000-04-05', 'en', 'Best friends since they were kids, Rabbi Jacob Schram (Ben Stiller) and Father Brian Finn (Edward Norton) are dynamic and popular young men living and working on New York\'s Upper West Side. When Anna Reilly (Jenna Elfman), once their childhood friend and now grown into a beautiful corporate executive, suddenly returns to the city, she reenters Jake and Brian\'s lives and hearts with a vengeance. Sparks fly and an unusual and complicated love triangle ensues.', '16620'),
