(1199, 'Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'The discovery of a mysterious camcorder leads to supernatural terror in a couple\'s new home.', '065', 2015, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '120', 'MV005049820000', '10143620', '2015-10-23', 'en', 'Ryan Fleege (Chris J. Murray), his wife Emily (Brit Shaw) and their 7-year-old daughter Leila (Ivy George) are preparing for Christmas in their new home. After finding an old and mysterious camcorder, Ryan quickly learns that it can record strange apparitions that are invisible to the naked eye. When young Leila starts talking to an imaginary friend and displaying strange behavior, the couple soon find themselves in a terrifying battle with a supernatural force.', '11867'),
(1200, 'Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'The discovery of a mysterious camcorder leads to supernatural terror in a couple\'s new home.', '104', 2015, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '120', 'MV005049820000', '10143620', '2015-10-23', 'en', 'Ryan Fleege (Chris J. Murray), his wife Emily (Brit Shaw) and their 7-year-old daughter Leila (Ivy George) are preparing for Christmas in their new home. After finding an old and mysterious camcorder, Ryan quickly learns that it can record strange apparitions that are invisible to the naked eye. When young Leila starts talking to an imaginary friend and displaying strange behavior, the couple soon find themselves in a terrifying battle with a supernatural force.', '11867'),
(1201, 'Chloe', 'Drama,Thriller,Romance,', 'A suspicious woman hires a prostitute to find out if her husband is cheating on her.', '557', 2009, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:40Z', '100', 'MV002730530000', '7996833', '2009-09-18', 'en', 'Catherine and David Stewart (Julianne Moore, Liam Neeson) are a well-to-do couple living in a posh area of Toronto, but all is not well in paradise. Catherine suspects that David, a music professor, is cheating on her with his students. She hires a prostitute named Chloe (Amanda Seyfried) to meet David and see if he gives in to temptation, but events spin out of control when Chloe spills the details of her torrid encounters.', '25272'),
(1202, 'Ad Astra', 'Science fiction,Adventure,Thriller,', 'An astronaut journeys across the universe to uncover the truth about his father\'s doomed mission.', '523', 2019, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:05Z', '125', 'MV011767610000', '15724355', '2019-08-29', 'en', 'Thirty years ago, Clifford McBride led a voyage into deep space, but the ship and crew were never heard from again. Now his son -- a fearless astronaut -- must embark on a daring mission to Neptune to uncover the truth about his missing father and a mysterious power surge that threatens the stability of the universe.', '18432'),
(1203, 'Hall Pass', 'Comedy,', 'Two men get permission from their wives to spend one week doing whatever they please.', '541', 2011, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:45Z', '105', 'MV003358360000', '8329415', '2011-02-25', 'en', 'Best friends Rick (Owen Wilson) and Fred (Jason Sudeikis) each have been married for a long time, and they are showing signs of restlessness. To revitalize their marriages, their wives (Jenna Fischer, Christina Applegate) grant them one week to do whatever they please, no questions asked. At first, the deal sounds like a dream come true, but as the week marches on, the two friends discover that their expectations are wildly out of sync with reality.', '18434'),
(1204, 'Dead Silence', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'A man returns to his haunted hometown to unravel the mystery surrounding his wife\'s death.', '542', 2007, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:30Z', '90', 'MV001867680000', '164673', '2007-03-16', 'en', 'After his wife meets a grisly end, Jamie Ashen (Ryan Kwanten) returns to their creepy hometown of Ravens Fair to unravel the mystery of her murder. Once there, he discovers the legend of Mary Shaw (Joan Heney), a murdered ventriloquist whose eerie presence still looms over the town. As he desperately digs for answers, Jamie encounters the curse that took his wife\'s life and threatens his own.', '18436'),
(1205, 'See No Evil', 'Horror,', 'A maniac (Kane) terrorizes a group of delinquents cleaning a hotel for community service.', '519', 2006, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:30Z', '90', 'MV001776670000', '160412', '2006-05-19', 'en', 'A reclusive maniac (Kane) terrorizes a group of young petty criminals who have arrived to clean up a rotting hotel as part of their community service. After one of them is kidnapped, the petrified group must find a way to fight off a seemingly unstoppable foe.', '10242'),
(1206, 'F/X', 'Thriller,Action,', 'Agents hire a special-effects man (Bryan Brown) to stage a fake mob hit.', '299', 1986, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:30Z', '150', 'MV000195820000', '9023', '1986-11-15', 'en', 'Rollie Tyler (Bryan Brown) is a special-effects expert for low-budget Hollywood movies. As gangster Nicholas DeFranco (Jerry Orbach) prepares to testify in court against his former bosses, FBI agents, fearing Nicholas will be killed by the mob before he can take the stand, decide to fake his assassination. The agents hire Rollie to use his special-effects skills to make the murder look believable. Leo McCarthy (Brian Dennehy), a detective, steps in to investigate the murder.', '28506'),
(1207, 'Liar Liar', 'Comedy,', 'A boy\'s wish comes true that his neglectful father will not be able to tell a lie for 24 hours.', '050', 1997, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '120', 'MV000499840000', '19140', '1997-03-21', 'en', 'Conniving attorney Fletcher Reede (Jim Carrey) is an ace in the courtroom, but his dishonesty and devotion to work ruin his relationships. His wife, Audrey (Maura Tierney), has left him for a more dependable man, and Fletcher often breaks the commitments he makes to his beloved son, Max (Justin Cooper). When Max wishes his dad would stop lying for 24 hours, Fletcher suddenly finds that he can only speak the truth -- on the day his career-deciding court case has to be won.', '11218'),
(1208, 'Liar Liar', 'Comedy,', 'A boy\'s wish comes true that his neglectful father will not be able to tell a lie for 24 hours.', '117', 1997, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '120', 'MV000499840000', '19140', '1997-03-21', 'en', 'Conniving attorney Fletcher Reede (Jim Carrey) is an ace in the courtroom, but his dishonesty and devotion to work ruin his relationships. His wife, Audrey (Maura Tierney), has left him for a more dependable man, and Fletcher often breaks the commitments he makes to his beloved son, Max (Justin Cooper). When Max wishes his dad would stop lying for 24 hours, Fletcher suddenly finds that he can only speak the truth -- on the day his career-deciding court case has to be won.', '11218'),
(1209, 'La muerte de un gallero', 'Western,Musical,', 'Dos hombres luchan por el amor y cariño de la misma mujer en la forma de una pelea de gallos.', '935', 1977, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T06:45Z', '105', 'MV000237570000', '49444', '1977', 'es', 'Un cacique golpea a su joven esposa y como venganza su enamorado entrena a un gallo para matar a su rival.', '47499'),
(1210, 'Victory at Sea', 'Documentary,', 'Alexander Scourby narrates World War II naval footage edited from the 1952 TV series.', '222', 1954, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:00Z', '120', 'MV000027450000', '37594', '1954', 'en', 'Originally a 26-episode television series that was broadcast during 1952 and 1953, this documentary consists largely of newsreels filmed during the naval campaigns of World War II. Along with the battle footage, scenes of everyday life on aircraft carriers and battleships alternate with poignant tableaux, such as an injured seaman being administered last rites by the onboard chaplain. Somber narration by Alexander Scourby and a score by Broadway composer Robert Russell Bennett complete the film.', '97163'),
(1211, 'Santa Fe Trail', 'Western,', 'Jeb Stuart (Errol Flynn) and West Pointers go to Kansas to stop John Brown (Raymond Massey).', '1260', 1940, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T07:30Z', '150', 'MV000023350000', '1454', '1940-12-28', 'en', 'After graduating from West Point, Jeb Stuart (Errol Flynn) and George Custer (Ronald Reagan) are both stationed to Fort Leavenworth in Kansas. Once there, they find that the violent abolitionist John Brown (Raymond Massey) has laid waste to the state, killing anyone who gets in the way of his anti-slavery crusade. While the duo must work together to battle the murderous revolutionary, they also come to blows over their competing love for Kit Carson Holliday (Olivia de Havilland).', '43926'),
(1212, 'Ocean Oasis', 'Documentary,', 'Filmmaker Soames Summerhays examines the ecology of Mexico\'s Sea of Cortès and Baja California.', '917', 2000, '2020-10-24T05:00Z', '2020-10-24T05:41Z', '41', 'MV001456270000', '83699', '2000', 'en', 'Filmmaker Soames Summerhays examines the ecology of Mexico\'s Sea of Cortès and Baja California.', '102442');
